ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectWheat, amber durum wheat and designated barley pool accounts 2010-2011 and for the feed barley pool B 2011 ** INTERIM PAYMENT **
PrecisOrder authorizing and directing the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to make INTERIM PAYMENTS in respect of wheat, amber durum wheat, and designated barley purchased by it during the pool period commencing on August 1, 2010 and terminating on July 31, 2011, and in respect of barley purchased by it during the pool period commencing on February 1, 2011 and terminating on July 31, 2011.
